results.title: Wasmtime
results.summary: Wasmtime is a standalone JIT-style runtime for WebAssembly, designed to be fast and secure. It allows developers to run WebAssembly modules in various environments, including servers and browsers.

results.title: Firecrawl - The Web Data API for AI
results.summary: Firecrawl is a web crawling, scraping, and search API designed for AI applications. It provides clean, structured data from the web, enabling developers to build powerful AI solutions.

results.title: Firecrawl Dashboard
results.summary: The Firecrawl dashboard offers users a comprehensive interface to manage their web scraping tasks, monitor performance, and access data insights in real-time.

results.title: The Topos of Music
results.summary: This book explores the geometric logic of concepts, theory, and performance in music, authored by Guerino Mazzola. It presents a comprehensive mathematical investigation into music, integrating various levels of musical description.
